race.description: Tab Regional Champs Fnl - Western Mbl Pce (L)
race.comment: There was plenty to like about the resuming effort of SWEET NATE (2) when he came from the back row for second in the heats. That took his record at this circuit and distance to two wins and two placings from four attempts and he'll better for it. A good draw could see him go one better. Hard to knock the recent consistency of BABY YOUR THE ONE (3) who added to a string of wins and placings by leading to win last week's heat by 5m. Draws to push forward again and she has built a strong record here so expect her to go close. SEASIDER (8) draws wide but he did a good job to win his heat when resuming last week and his strike rate at this circuit and distance stands at 50 per cent. HUNTER SHANNON (7) came from a similar draw to chase BABY YOUR THE ONE as runner-up last week, his fifth placing from his last six starts. He deserves respect while the ace draw brings ART OF TERROR (1) into calculations.
